Recommends: mosquitto, gpsd
Description: Driver Monitoring & Fleet Navigation System
 Wake Focus is a production-grade, cross-platform desktop application
 for real-time driver monitoring, distraction detection, and fleet
 navigation with incident-aware rerouting.
 .
 Features:
  - Real-time drowsiness detection (MediaPipe Face Mesh + EAR)
  - Object distraction detection (YOLO26)
  - GPS tracking with fleet communication (MQTT)
  - Incident-aware rerouting (OSRM)
  - Cross-platform: Windows, Linux x86_64, ARM64
